00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:46.050
As a professor of Chinese
philosophy, international history

00:05:46.050 --> 00:05:50.810
and religion and of
Confucianism, in particular,

00:05:50.810 --> 00:05:54.360
I would like to introduce
Confucianism,

00:05:54.360 --> 00:06:00.500
one of the great traditions
in the world to everyone here.

00:06:00.500 --> 00:06:06.470
